{"tid":1833193,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"錯過兩對好平嘅平底鞋有感","createTime":"2020-01-21T17:10:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T17:31:03.000Z","uid":28240,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f1f4836812e3ebee81ff49ffc10b349b2435700c","tid":1833193,"uid":28240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T17:10:45.000Z","msg":"我今日錯過左兩對鞋 <br />\n然後俾男朋友寸 <br />\n一對$177 屬於港女牌oriental traffic 嘅黑色令面鞋 <br />\n另一對係啡色無印鞋 $250<br />\n前幾日見到 <br />\n覺得可以等多陣先買<br />\n點知今日去舖頭睇俾人買Q曬<br />\n女人買嘢嘅速度果然係世上第一<br />\n可惜我兩對鞋都買唔到<br />\n只可以繼續著住對行路覺得少腳痛嘅平底鞋<br />\n買鞋就好似搵男朋友咁<br />\n可一不可再<br />\n錯過左就無嫁啦<br />\n呢個故事教訓我見到平靚正嘅嘢要立即入手<br />\n如果唔係蘇州過後無艇搭<br />\n到頭來兩頭空 悲哉 悲哉"},{"pid":"68861e059de21a62338191feea1484e98b4d447a","tid":1833193,"uid":129658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T17:12:15.000Z","msg":"下甘即係典-.-"},{"pid":"c02d41334c6662adcf2a2e3765c1083316914f49","tid":1833193,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T17:14:06.000Z","msg":"著嚟格劍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"765ef136ebf5cb65e81c35d86fe9bb0993788178","tid":1833193,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T17:14:17.000Z","msg":"傻閪"},{"pid":"96945e5f00e64d799484cc1fb5c3eb4ee75742b9","tid":1833193,"uid":226573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T17:14:47.000Z","msg":"唔買無所印住個時想等啲咩？"},{"pid":"01df534a4ce281496eaa17c228a6ada391ffd7f6","tid":1833193,"uid":226573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T17:15:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔買無印住個時想等啲咩？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7f223ac117bf363e964ea03bf829889a12698a39","tid":1833193,"uid":70417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T17:18:15.000Z","msg":"oriental traffic果款特價左好撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d4c60ebf9f474e6a1a3140726baea6ee7f4e4d7","tid":1833193,"uid":28240,"like":0